===Adjective===
'''fet, -are, -ast'''
*{{IPA|/feːt/}}
#[[fat]], [[obese]] (''about people or animals'')
#:'''''Fetare''' gubbe har jag nog aldrig sett tidigare.''
#:''I don't think I've seen such a fat geezer before.''
#containing much [[fat]] (''about food'')
#being especially [[fertile]], [[profitable]] or [[lucrative]]; (''slang'') [[good]], [[extraordinary]], [[phat]] (''a general positive intensifier'')
#:''Du missade en riktigt '''fet''' chans.''
#:"You missed quite a good opportunity.'''
#:''Shit, vilken '''fet''' bil du har köpt!''
#:''Damn, what a nice/cool/phat you've bought!''

